title: Tears of the Kingdom News Roundup, Interest in a Zelda Movie, & More! | IGN The Weekly Fix
description:
Wanna catch up on all the gaming and entertainment news highlights from the past week? From a roundup of the first week of news for The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom, to there being interest in a Zelda Movie at Nintendo, tune in for the Weekly Fix - the only show packed with the recommended weekly dose of gaming, entertainment, and esports news!

08:57 - Can Assassin's Creed Save Ubisoft?

description:
Take a look at the latest trailer for The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom showing off the game's critical reception. The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom is available now for Nintendo Switch.

title: The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom - 9 MORE Things to Do First
description:
Did you do all of the things we listed in our previous "Things to Do First," video? Well we've got 9 more things that you should do once you're about on dungeon deep in Zelda Tears of the Kingdom that will help you get on the right foot when preparing for the remainder of the game.

title: Dead by Daylight - Official End Transmission Trailer
description:
What once aided our survival, became the catalyst of our destruction. Check out the trailer for Dead by Daylight's End Transmission Chapter, which brings The Singularity, Gabriel Soma, and the Toba Landing Map to the multiplayer action/horror game. Dead by Daylight's End Transmission Chapter will be available on June 13, 2023.
